These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, funk
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, western
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, amber
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, cycling
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bongani
1. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
2. the mechanic is on the far right##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is the person who likes amber##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Music-Genre      | funk     | jazz       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | sudoku     |
| Job           | fisherman | mechanic   |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | superhero  |
| Color   | amber | blood-red |
| Sport           | basketball      | cycling     |
| Cigar     | bongani    | siglo   |

