.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different games are played: go, backgammon
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, drawing
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, german
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, satire
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, june
1. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person watching satire movies is the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the german is on the far right##1
5. the person playing go is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Game      | go    | backgammon |
| Hobby         | drawing        | dancing  |
| Flower           | sunflower | aconite  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b            | indie    |
| Nationality   | australian     | german   |
| Movie-Genre           | musical         | satire    |
| Birthday     | october           | june      |

