.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, egyptian
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, strawberry
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, journalist
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, march
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, techno
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daisy
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, skateboard
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the dancer is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Nationality      | russian          | egyptian       |
| Food          | strawberry   | eggplant   |
| Job           | journalist   | dancer     |
| Birthday   | july | march        |
| Music-Genre           | disco      | techno       |
| Flower         | balloon-flower       | daisy |
